OL,3,CNoel Clarke loses libel case against
OL,4,CThe Guardian publisher
OL,6,FActor Noel Clarke has lost his libel
OL,7,Fclaim against The Guardian's publisher
OL,8,Fover its reporting of misconduct
OL,9,Fallegations.
OL,11,FThe 49-year-old sued Guardian News and
OL,12,FMedia (GNM) over seven articles and a
OL,13,Fpodcast, including an article in April
OL,14,F2021 that said 20 women who knew him
OL,15,Fprofessionally had come forward with
OL,16,Fallegations of misconduct.
OL,18,FThe Doctor Who star denies the
OL,19,Fallegations, while GNM defended its
OL,20,Freporting as being both true and in
OL,21,Fthe public interest.
