OL,3,CNoel Clarke loses libel case against
OL,4,CThe Guardian publisher
OL,6,FMrs Justice Steyn agreed, dismissing
OL,7,FClarke's claim in a judgment on
OL,8,FFriday, saying that the newspaper
OL,9,F"succeeded in establishing both truth
OL,10,Fand public interest defences to the
OL,11,Flibel claim".
OL,13,FShe added: "I have accepted some of Mr
OL,14,FClarke's evidence... but overall I
OL,15,Ffind that he was not a credible or
OL,16,Freliable witness."
