OL,3,CNoel Clarke loses libel case against
OL,4,CThe Guardian publisher
OL,6,FThe High Court in London heard
OL,7,Fevidence from multiple witnesses who
OL,8,Fmade accusations against Clarke,
OL,9,Fincluding that he had allegedly shared
OL,10,Fnude photographs of them without their
OL,11,Fconsent, groped them, and asked them
OL,12,Fto look at him when he was exposed.
OL,14,FBarristers for Clarke told the court
OL,15,Fthat there was a conspiracy of people
OL,16,Fwith financial and personal grudges
OL,17,Fagainst him who engineered his
OL,18,Fdownfall because they could not bear
OL,19,Fto see him receive a Bafta award.
