OL,6,FShe said: "Mr Clarke's case that there
OL,7,Fis an unlawful means conspiracy
OL,8,Fagainst him, in which many of the
OL,9,Fwitnesses, and some non-witnesses, are
OL,10,Fsaid to have engaged, was born of
OL,11,Fnecessity, in the face of the large
OL,12,Fbody of witnesses giving evidence
OL,13,Fagainst him.
