OL,6,F"This is also a landmark judgment for
OL,7,FGuardian journalism, and for
OL,8,Finvestigative journalism in Britain.
OL,9,FIt was important to fight this case.
OL,11,F"This was a deeply-researched
OL,12,Finvestigation by some of the
OL,13,FGuardian's best reporters, who worked
OL,14,Fdiligently and responsibly. The
OL,15,Fjudgment is clear that our
OL,16,Finvestigation was thorough and fair, a
OL,17,Ftemplate for public interest
OL,18,Fjournalism.
